{
  "texts": [
    "1 Framework of the proposed APP-DGNN for academic performance prediction For IGCN in APP-DGNN, we have L s layers of GCN, so the complexity is O(L s (|E|d i d o)).",
    "For AGCN in APP-DGNN, there are L layers of RGCN, which consist of GCN and GAT modules.",
    "The complexity of the GCN module is O(L|E|d i d o).",
    "The complexity of the GAT module is O(L(N d i d o + |E|d o + d m d o)), where d m is the number of neurons in the MLP layer for attention coefficients.",
    "The complexity of k-NN module is O(L N 2 d i)."
  ]
}